                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <br />
    <br />

    <div class="content">
        <h1>ABOUT US</h1>

        <br />
        <br />

        <p>
            KhumaloCraft is a platform dedicated to showcasing handcrafted products from artisans around the world.
            Our vision is to connect artisans from around the world, offering a diverse range of unique and high-quality products.
            Founded by James Khumalo, our platform aims to provide a scalable, accessible, and user-friendly experience
            for both artisans and shoppers alike.
